 Live Aid发起人猛烈抨击那些对Band Aid单曲有异议的“好管闲事、唤醒人们和行善者” https://www.nme.com/news/music/live-aid-promoter-hits-out-at-busybodies-and-woke-people-and-do-gooders-who-have-an-issue-with-创可贴-单-3815596？u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=live-aid-promoter-hits-out-at-busybodies-and-woke-people-and-do-gooders-who-have-an-issue-with-band-aid-singleLaura Molloy Mon, 25 Nov 2024 13:58:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsChristmasPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3815596 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他们知道今天是圣诞节吗？”因延续对非洲的“破坏性刻板印象”而受到审查</p><p>《Live Aid》的发起人猛烈抨击了那些对<a href="https://www.nme.com">《</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/live-aid-promoter-hits-out-at-busybodies-and-woke-people-and-do-gooders-who-have-an-issue-with-band-aid-single-3815596">Band Aid》单曲有异议的“好管闲事、唤醒人们和行善者”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Singers-recording-Do-They-Know-its-Christmas-for-Band-Aid-at-Basing-St-Studios-November-26th-1984.-CREDIT_-Steve-Hurrell_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Live Aid 的发起人回应了最近对 Band Aid 慈善单曲“Do They Know It&#39;s Christmas?”的批评，称那些对这首歌提出异议的人是“多管闲事、唤醒人们和行善者”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/worst-christmas-number-one-singles-2166937">从档案中——有史以来最糟糕的圣诞节头号人物</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首慈善单曲最初由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-geldof">Bob Geldof</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/midge-ure">Midge Ure</a>于 1984 年构思，旨在为埃塞俄比亚饥荒筹集资金。此后，该曲目的另外两个版本分别于 2004 年和 2014 年发行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/all-star-2024-ulimate-mix-of-band-aids-do-they-know-its-christmas-coming-later-this-month-3812230">今天推出了原歌曲 40 周年纪念合辑</a>，汇集了所有三个版本的所有声音，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">斯汀</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boy-george">Boy George</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-smith">Sam Smith</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">Harry Styles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-martin">Chris Martin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elbow">Elbow</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guy-garvey">Guy Garvey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sugababes">Sugababes</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bananarama">Bananarama</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seal">海豹、</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnr">西妮德·奥康纳</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rita-ora">丽塔·奥拉</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kool-and-the-gang">库尔帮</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/underworld">黑社会</a>等。</p><p>然而，在 2014 年版本的艾德·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">希兰 (Ed Sheeran</a> ) 表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-would-have-declined-new-band-aid-single-didnt-ask-permission-3813639">2024 年版本并未征求他的许可后，</a>慈善单曲“Ultimate Mix”的发行前夕陷入了争议。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-would-have-declined-new-band-aid-single-didnt-ask-permission-3813639">如果是的话，他会恭敬地拒绝</a>。 </p><p><iframe title="创可贴 - 他们知道今天是圣诞节吗？ （官方视频）[4K]" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RH-xd5bPKTA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在 Instagram 上分享的一份声明中，希兰提到了加纳裔英国艺术家 Fuse ODG<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/various-artists-1301-1220230">拒绝参与该歌曲 2014 年版的制作</a>。富斯在推理中解释了为非洲筹集资金的努力如何导致非洲大陆“长期存在破坏性的刻板印象”。</p><p>希兰补充道：“十年过去了，我对与此相关的叙述的理解已经改变，”他写道。 “这只是我个人的立场，我希望这是一个前瞻性的立场。”</p><p>现在，该曲目的发起人 Harvey Goldsmith 在今天（11 月 25 日）接受<em>时代电台</em>采访时对 Sheeran 和 Fuse 的评论做出了回应。</p><p>戈德史密斯告诉电视台：“我们想做点什么来提供帮助。就这么简单。所有这些爱管闲事的人，唤醒了那些无所不知的人们和行善者，让他们出去做点什么。”他还批评媒体“试图把事情夸大到事实并非如此”。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：他们知道今天是圣诞节吗？ - 2024 年终极组合" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/3cK10zROGQYpqa3vsU6bs9?go=1&#038;sp_cid=9e4dd2003a91fbea76cc4926ca690581&#038;utm_source=oembed&#038;utm_medium=desktop"></iframe></p><p>戈德史密斯特别提到希兰，表示这位歌手“有权拥有自己的声音”，但他补充道：“40 年过去了，我们仍在收到资金。我们仍然分发它们。我们只将它们分发给项目。我们不会在任何地方资助任何类型的管理费用。我们正在尽力做到最好。如果他们不喜欢，那就很难了。”</p><p>除了 Fuse ODG 和 Sheeran 之外，埃塞俄比亚总理阿比·艾哈迈德 (Abiy Ahmed) 也公开谈论了这条赛道的潜在负面影响。艾哈迈德承认最初的版本“当时是善意的”，但他补充说，“看到我们国家的古老历史、文化、多样性和美丽沦为厄运和阴郁，令人沮丧”。</p><p>他还表示，虽然创可贴的人道主义努力“令人钦佩且值得赞赏”，但他认为它“没有与时俱进，并且最终可能弊大于利”。</p><p>希兰发表声明后，一位接近创可贴的消息人士告诉<em>《NME》</em> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-geldof-has-put-a-call-in-to-ed-sheeran-over-band-aid-single-controversy-theyll-work-it-out-3814078">格尔多夫已就此事亲自与希兰联系</a>。这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-boomtown-rats">Boomtown Rats</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-geldof-responds-to-ed-sheerans-band-aid-comments-this-little-pop-song-has-kept-millions-of-people-alive-3815381">后来向《<em>星期日泰晤士报》</em>做出了回应</a>，他说：“这首小流行歌曲让数百万人活了下来。”</p><p>格尔多夫继续说道：“为什么创可贴会放弃为数千名依赖我们吃饭的儿童提供食物？为什么不继续这样做呢？因为抽象的富裕世界论点，无论其合法性如何？</p><p>他补充道：“任何抽象理论，无论多么真诚地持有，都不应妨碍或分散人们对可怕而具体的现实世界的注意力。” “世界上有 6 亿饥饿人口，其中 3 亿在非洲。我们希望是其他的，但事实并非如此。我们可以帮助其中一些人。这就是我们将继续做的事情。”</p><p>自从新的“Ultimate Mix”发布以来，人们一直在社交媒体上做出反应。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-ultimate-mix-of-band-aids-do-they-know-its-christmas-released-fans-react-3815587">您可以在此处查看一些回复</a>。</p><p> 《Live Aid》的发起人猛烈抨击了那些对<a href="https://www.nme.com">《</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/live-aid-promoter-hits-out-at-busybodies-and-woke-people-and-do-gooders-who-have-an-issue-with-band-aid-single-3815596">Band Aid》单曲有异议的“好管闲事、唤醒人们和行善者”</a> 。</p> ;
 Paul Heaton、Travis、Echo & The Bunnymen 和 Faithless 宣布哈利法克斯 2025 年夏季大型演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-travis-echo-the-bunnymen-faithless-halifax-summer-2025-headline-shows-3815599?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=paul-heaton-travis-echo-the-bunnymen-faithless-halifax-summer-2025-headline-showsLiberty Dunworth Mon, 25 Nov 2024 13:46:39 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicIndieLive Music NewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3815599 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《Echo &amp; the Bunnymen》的伊恩·麦卡洛克、《特拉维斯》的弗兰·希利、《Faithless》的斯坦·怀特和保罗·希顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>来自 Billy Bragg、The Magic Numbers 等的支持</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-travis-echo-the-bunnymen-faithless-halifax-summer-2025-headline-shows-3815599">Paul Heaton、Travis、Echo &amp; The Bunnymen 和 Faithless 宣布 2025 年哈利法克斯夏季大型演出的头条新闻</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《Echo &amp; the Bunnymen》的伊恩·麦卡洛克、《特拉维斯》的弗兰·希利、《Faithless》的斯坦·怀特和保罗·希顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Halifax@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>哈利法克斯 Piece Hall 宣布了 2025 年夏季的四场新的头条演出，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-heaton">Paul Heaton</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis">Travis</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/echo-and-the-bunnymen">Echo &amp; The Bunnymen</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faithless">Faithless</a>的表演。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-single-gaslight-and-talk-new-album-l-a-times-america-is-so-wrapped-in-their-own-history-3604566"><b>特拉维斯分享单曲《Gaslight》并谈论新专辑《洛杉矶时报》：“美国如此沉浸在自己的历史中”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>作为 2025 年 TK Maxx 在 The Piece Hall 举行的现场演出的一部分，今天（11 月 25 日）已确认四位新的领军人物，他们将在 2025 年 7 月至 8 月期间进行演出。</p><p>新宣布的第一位登台表演者是保罗·希顿 (Paul Heaton)，他的演出时间为 7 月 23 日。这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-housemartins">Housemartins</a>主唱的嘉宾歌手瑞安·唐尼 (Rianne Downey) 也将加入他的行列，她将在他的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-announces-new-ian-broudie-produced-album-the-mighty-several-and-uk-tour-with-the-zutons-3767640">《The Mighty Been》</a>中献唱。特邀嘉宾包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-bragg">比利·布拉格 (Billy Bragg)</a> 。</p><p>继今年早些时候发行最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-single-gaslight-and-talk-new-album-l-a-times-america-is-so-wrapped-in-their-own-history-3604566">《LA Times》</a>之后，格拉斯哥乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis">Travis</a>将于 7 月 26 日作为头条新闻登上舞台。该节目是他们今年早些时候开始的一系列节目的后续节目，水星奖提名者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-magic-numbers">《神奇数字》</a>也加入了他们的行列。</p><p>利物浦摇滚偶像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/echo-and-the-bunnymen">Echo &amp; The Bunnymen</a>将于 8 月 9 日成为头条新闻，这一消息发布之际，他们正准备庆祝经典专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-849-336771">《What Are You Going To Do With Your Life?》</a>发行 25 周年。本周晚些时候。 </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="🚨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />另外四位轰动的头条新闻确认将在 2025 年 The Piece Hall 举办<a href="https://twitter.com/TKMaxx_UK?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@TKMaxx_UK</a>现场演出 – <a href="https://twitter.com/PaulHeatonSolo?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@PaulHeatonSolo</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/TravisBand?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@TravisBand</a> 、Echo &amp; the <a href="https://twitter.com/Bunnymen?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Bunnymen</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/faithless?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Faithless</a> ！ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f929.png" alt="🤩" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>门票周五上午 9 点发售Club 1779 会员可于周二上午 9 点获得预售权限。在这里注册<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f449.png" alt="👉" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/ZrHIxoR4fl">https://t.co/ZrHIxoR4fl</a> <a href="https://t.co/D2M3JfnwV7">pic.twitter.com/D2M3JfnwV7</a></p><p> — The Piece Hall (@ThePieceHall) <a href="https://twitter.com/ThePieceHall/status/1860973034741321823?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 11 月 25 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>最后，电子音乐传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faithless">Faithless</a>完成了明年夏天 The Piece Hall 确认的新头条人物名单。该曲目定于 8 月 22 日演出，距离他们广受好评的首张专辑《Reverence》发行已近 30 年，并且乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-announce-2024-champion-sound-uk-and-european-tour-3787512">本月将进行英国和欧洲巡演</a>。</p><p> Piece Hall 慈善信托基金首席执行官尼基·钱斯·汤普森 MBE DL 在一份新声明中表示：“另一批截然不同的预订保证会让观众随着一些绝对经典的歌曲一起跳舞和唱歌。”</p><p> “保罗·希顿非凡的歌曲创作技巧意味着我们将听到一堆制作精美、常常古怪且总是朗朗上口的歌曲。同样，特拉维斯 (Travis) 的 90 年代标志性专辑中也有大量的长唱歌曲，这些歌曲将在庭院中响起，”汤普森补充道。</p><p> “我想在我们的场地听到传奇人物 Echo 和 Bunnymen 精彩独特的声音已经有一段时间了。当 Faithless 带着令人振奋和赞歌般的声音走上舞台时，高举双手的时刻是 100% 保证的。我已经等不及夏天了！” </p><figure id="attachment_3815606" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3815606" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3815606" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="弗兰·希利（Fran Healy），特拉维斯乐队主唱" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3815606" class="wp-caption-text">弗兰·希利 (Fran Healy)，2024 年特拉维斯 (Travis) 主唱。图片来源：Pedro Becerra/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>对 Echo &amp; The Bunnymen 和 Faithless 的支持演出将于稍后公布，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Ftk-maxx-presents-live-at-the-tickets%2Fartist%2F5364605" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处获取所有演出的门票</a>。</p><p>随着今天的宣布，新一批艺术家加入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Weezer">Weezer 的</a>行列，Weezer 上周宣布该节目<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezer-announce-only-uk-headline-show-of-2025-with-bad-nerves-and-more-3812077">将成为他们明年唯一的英国头条节目</a>。 Bad Nerves 和 Teen Morgage 等乐队将担任开场支持。</p><p>排队的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/James">James</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Libertines">The Libertines</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Simple-Minds">Simple Minds</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Khruangbin">Khruangbin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Texas">Texas</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Olly-Murs">Olly Murs</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Rag-n-Bone-Man">Rag&#39;n&#39;Bone Man</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/UB40">UB40</a> ft Ali Campbell、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Dean-Lewis">Dean Lewis</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Script">The Script</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-travis-echo-the-bunnymen-faithless-halifax-summer-2025-headline-shows-3815599">Paul Heaton、Travis、Echo &amp; The Bunnymen 和 Faithless 宣布 2025 年哈利法克斯夏季大型演出的头条新闻</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
凯拉·奈特莉表示，她因拍摄《加勒比海盗》电影而被“视为狗屎” https://www.nme.com/news/film/keira-knightley-says-she-was-seen-as-shit-for-doing-pirates-of-the-caribbean-films-3815583?ut m_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=keira-knightley-说她因为拍加勒比海盗电影而被视为狗屎Damian JonesMon, 25 Nov 2024 13:43:35 +0000 Film NewsNewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3815583 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯拉·奈特莉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位女演员在前三部电影中饰演伊丽莎白·斯旺，取得了突破</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/keira-knightley-says-she-was-seen-as-shit-for-doing-pirates-of-the-caribbean-films-3815583">凯拉·奈特莉 (Keira Knightley) 表示，她因拍摄《加勒比海盗》电影而被“视为狗屎”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯拉·奈特莉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_keiraknightley_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keira-knightley">凯拉·奈特莉</a>讲述了她在<em>加勒比海盗</em>电影中的工作经历。</p><p>这位女演员在 2003 年至 2007 年的前三部电影中饰演伊丽莎白·斯旺 (Elizabeth Swann)，取得了突破。</p><p>奈特莉在一次新的采访中表示，尽管她和特许经营权取得了成功，但她对自己在其中的角色有着复杂的感觉，尽管她有机会继续做更好的事情。</p><p>她告诉<a href="https://www.thetimes.com/life-style/celebrity/article/keira-knightley-turning-40-black-doves-0pt7gcdjh"><em>《泰晤士报》</em></a> ：“当你同时拥有一些成就和摧毁你的东西时，这是一件有趣的事情。因为他们，我被视为垃圾，但因为他们做得很好，我有机会拍摄那些我最终获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>提名的电影。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_piratesofthecaribbean_disney_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> 《加勒比海盗：世界的尽头》中的伊丽莎白·斯旺（凯拉·奈特莉饰）和杰克·斯派洛（约翰尼·德普饰）图片来源：迪士尼/天空电视台</figcaption></figure><p>“它们是我参与过的最成功的电影，也是我被公开贬低的原因。所以它们在我的脑海中是一个非常混乱的地方。”</p><p>奈特莉还排除了出现在未来任何<em>加勒比海盗</em>电影中的可能性，并补充道：“时间太疯狂了。这是你生命中的岁月，你无法控制在哪里拍摄、拍摄多长时间、拍摄什么。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/keira-knightley-rules-out-pirates-of-the-caribbean-return-3414186">去年当被问及重返球队</a>时，她也发表了类似的评论。</p><p>与此同时，理查德·柯蒂斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/richard-curtis-would-cast-someone-older-keira-knightley-made-love-actually-today-3549758">最近表示，如果他今天拍<em>《真爱至上》，</em>他会找比奈特莉年长的人来扮演她的角色</a>。</p><p>在 2003 年的浪漫喜剧中，奈特莉饰演朱丽叶时年仅 18 岁，朱丽叶嫁给了由 26 岁的切瓦特·埃加福特饰演的彼得。与此同时，爱上朱丽叶的马克由 30 岁的安德鲁·林肯扮演。</p><p>奈特莉接下来将主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a>间谍惊悚片<em>《黑鸽子</em>》，该片将于 12 月 5 日登陆英国和美国流媒体服务。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="黑鸽子|官方预告片 #2 | Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/shzJzjVscno?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>根据<a href="https://www.netflix.com/tudum/articles/black-doves-netflix"><em>Tudum 的</em></a>剧情简介，这部电影“以圣诞节的伦敦为背景”<em> </em>这是一个“关于友谊和牺牲的尖锐、充满动作、真挚的故事”。</p><p>故事讲述的是韦伯（奈特莉饰），“一位机智、脚踏实地、尽职尽责的妻子和母亲，也是一名职业间谍。十年来，她一直将政治家丈夫的秘密传递给她工作的神秘组织：黑鸽子。当她的秘密情人杰森（安德鲁·科吉饰）被暗杀时，她的间谍头子、神秘的里德（莎拉·兰开夏饰）打电话给海伦的老朋友山姆（本·卫肖饰）来保护她的安全。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/keira-knightley-says-she-was-seen-as-shit-for-doing-pirates-of-the-caribbean-films-3815583">凯拉·奈特莉 (Keira Knightley) 表示，她因拍摄《加勒比海盗》电影而被“视为狗屎”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Bronski Beat 的吉米·萨默维尔 (Jimmy Somerville) 力争将“小镇男孩”从“反跨性别者”LGB 联盟的电影中删除：“我永远不会允许这样的团体使用我的任何东西” https://www.nme.com/news/music/bronski-beat-jimmy-somerville-to-remove-smalltown-boy-from-anti-trans-film-3815547?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bronski-beat-吉米·萨默维尔将从反跨性别电影中删除小镇男孩Laura MolloyMon, 25 Nov 2024 12:56:47 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3815547 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们将尽一切努力尽快将《小镇男孩》从这部电影中删除”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bronski-beat-jimmy-somerville-to-remove-smalltown-boy-from-anti-trans-film-3815547">Bronski Beat 的吉米·萨默维尔 (Jimmy Somerville) 为“反变性”LGB 联盟将《小镇男孩》从电影中删除而奋斗：“我永远不会允许我的任何东西被这样的团体使用”，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jimmy-Somerville.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Bronski Beat 的吉米·萨默维尔 (Jimmy Somerville) 发誓要将“小镇男孩”从“反跨性别”团体 LGB 联盟即将上映的电影中删除。</p><p>自 1984 年发行以来，这首歌一直被视为同性恋圣歌，并被认为为其他同性恋艺术家通过音乐分享他们的经历铺平了道路。</p><p> 《小镇男孩》的歌词和视频引起了人们对艾滋病流行期间恐同症的关注，萨默维尔扮演了一个被警察赶出家门并被赶出家门的小男孩。然后，他乘火车前往伦敦，与乐队其他成员一起在首都开始了新生活——描绘了当时 LGBTQ+ 年轻人的共同经历。</p><p>最近，有消息称 LGB 联盟正在即将上映的纪录片<em>《同性恋一代》</em>中使用这首歌曲。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bronski Beat - 小镇男孩（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/88sARuFu-tc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该组织于 2021 年获得慈善地位，声称“促进女同性恋、男同性恋和双性恋者的利益”，但一直直言不讳地表示排斥跨性别者，并反对学校的性别认同教育、性别认可改革和性别肯定的医疗保健。</p><p> Bronski Beat 的幸存成员萨默维尔昨天（11 月 24 日）在 Instagram 上表示，电影中使用这首歌曲“未经批准”。</p><p>萨默维尔在一段视频中说：“我注意到 LGB 联盟正在一部名为<em>《同性恋一代》</em>的电影中使用‘小镇男孩’。 LGB 联盟是反跨性别者的。我绝对不会允许我的任何东西被这样的团体利用。因此，我们将尽一切努力尽快将“小镇男孩”从这部电影中删除。</p><p> “你怎么敢？你他妈怎么敢？所以我只是想让你们知道，这与我无关，我不知道这件事，但我们会对此采取行动，”他总结道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permal